This paper involves computer vision techniques for recovering multispectral signals from RGB images, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). Additionally, the use of machine learning algorithms for training and validation suggests that it could also fall under the categories of multimedia (cs.MM), information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
